commit.message:
libstdc++: Document new libstdc++.so symbol versions

libstdc++-v3/ChangeLog:

	* doc/xml/manual/abi.xml: Document GLIBCXX_3.4.30 and
	GLIBCXX_3.4.31 versions.
	* doc/html/manual/abi.html: Regenerate.
